rl.photoviewer.model

Class PhotoMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • rl.photoviewer.model.PhotoMetadata
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<PhotoMetadata>

    public class PhotoMetadata
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<PhotoMetadata>
    Container for selected Exif metadata. Currently, for each photo the file name, caption, date, camera model, latitude and longitude values, as well as all keywords are stored.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde
